Format ED2IN tag-value list

Source: R/write_ed2in.R
tags2char.Rd

Converts an ed2in-like list to an ED2IN-formatted character vector.

Usage

tags2char(ed2in)

Arguments

ed2in

Named list of ED2IN tag-value pairs. See read_ed2in.
